              </h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6 line-clamp-3" data-ps="src/pages/journal/index.astro:65kvq1">
                {featuredPost.data.description}
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4" data-ps="src/pages/journal/index.astro:7upzwk">
